  <div id="apps">
  <h2>Must have apps to reduce food waste</h2>
    <p>Do your bit for the war on waste! If you <kbd>love food and hate waste</kbd> - download these apps to help tackle food waste</p>

<div class="row">
<div class="col-3"> 

    <div>
      <img src='http://citiesforlife-latribune.paris/Media/logo_too_good_to_go.png' class="rounded-circle img-fluid" >
      <p> The Too Good To Go app  links you with delicious food that would otherwise be thrown away for little money. You can order delicious food from local restaurants, cafes, bakeries and other food businesses, collect it up to an hour before closing time.</p>
      <a href="http://toogoodtogo.co.uk/" class="btn btn-info" role="button" target="_blank">Download Too Good To Go here</a>
    </div>

</div>

<div class="col-3">
    <div>
      <img src='http://is5.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple118/v4/d6/aa/58/d6aa5873-e92d-8487-3ce3-35e16ff2a626/source/1200x630bb.jpg' class="rounded-circle img-fluid">
      <p>OLIO connects app users to excess home-grown vegetables, food nearing its sell-by date in local shops, and any unwanted food in households. Users can upload a picture of their unwanted item and nearby neighbours and other users can pick these up for free!</p>
       <a href="https://olioex.com/" class="btn btn-info" role="button" target="_blank">Download OLIO here</a>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="col-3">
    <div>
      <img src='https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/839916529512755201/pILzIEJi.jpg' class="rounded-circle img-fluid">
      <p>YellowLabel is a UK wide app for discounted goods that are due to expire. The app prevents food waste and saves you money by advertising and enabling the sale of ‘Yellow Label’ goods at your local supermarket such as Marks and Spencers, Sainbury's or Tesco.</p>
      <a href="http://yellow-label.co.uk/" class="btn btn-info" role="button" target="_blank">Download YellowLabel here</a> 
    </div> 
</div>

<div class="col-3">
    <div>
      <img src='https://i.vimeocdn.com/portrait/17945325_300x300' class="rounded-circle img-fluid">
      <p>Love Food Hate Waste helps you to rethink how we shop, plan our meals better and use up our leftovers, thereby keepng foud out of the bin!</p>
      <a href="https://scotland.lovefoodhatewaste.com/" class="btn btn-info" role="button" target="_blank">Download Love Food Hate Waste here</a> 
    </div> 
</div>
</div>


