      <p>What's scarier than witches and ghosts at Halloween...? How about the ghoulstly 15 million pumpkins that are binned every Halloween, which is enough to make a bowl of pumpkin soup for everyone in Britain!? Find your nearest pumpkin rescue event and discover tasty simple ways to eat your pumpkin guts!</p>
